subject: Tennis
Rogers Cup (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Sabine Lisicki upset 13th-seeded Sara Errani, 6-1, 7-5, in Montreal in the first round of the Rogers Cup, the final tuneup ahead of the United States Open.
